Company Profile
Sector: Technology
Industry: Hardware
Sub-Industry: Computer Hardware & Storage
Pivot3, Inc. provides data storage solutions for video surveillance, content distribution, data archiving, backup, and secondary storage applications. The Company offers failover-protected virtual machines including scale-out disk storage appliance and supports various virtual servers and solid state disk drives. Pivot3 conducts its business internationally.




