Company Overview of Pivot3 Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Pivot3 Inc. provides hyper-converged infrastructure solutions for enterprise IT in the United States and internationally. The company’s hyper-converged platforms are used for high-performance workloads in data-intensive environments, such as virtual desktop infrastructure, video surveillance, disaster recovery, server virtualization, big data, data center consolidation, and remote and branch office. It offers vSTAC OS, a software that forms a virtual HyperSAN to unite and share storage and compute resources across various nodes and virtual machines to enable global hyper-convergence; Acuity, a software platform that simplifies workload management with policy-based management engine and compr...
Pivot3 Inc. provides hyper-converged infrastructure solutions for enterprise IT in the United States and internationally. The company’s hyper-converged platforms are used for high-performance workloads in data-intensive environments, such as virtual desktop infrastructure, video surveillance, disaster recovery, server virtualization, big data, data center consolidation, and remote and branch office. It offers vSTAC OS, a software that forms a virtual HyperSAN to unite and share storage and compute resources across various nodes and virtual machines to enable global hyper-convergence; Acuity, a software platform that simplifies workload management with policy-based management engine and comprehensive data services; Global Hyper-Converged Infrastructure (HCI) platforms that allow to pool various resources to compute, memory, and storage at scale to deliver HCI system in the market; and globally hyper-converged security platforms that are designed to ensure that various critical video surveillance streams are stored and protected. The company also provides professional services, technical support, and online support portal. It offers its products through distributors and resellers in the United States, Canada, Europe, the Middle East, Africa, Latin American, Caribbean, and the Asia Pacific. The company has a strategic partnership with Gotham Technology Group. Pivot3 Inc. was founded in 2002 and is based in Austin, Texas with additional offices in Derby, United Kingdom; Seoul, Korea; Dubai, United Arab Emirates; and Singapore. It also has a development center in Spring, Texas.
Detailed Description


