Pivot3, Inc.





















    
        
        
        

    
    
        
        
     
    

 

 Pivot3, Inc.





Pivot3 High-Definition Storage for video surveillance supports up to sixteen times the cameras at half the cost of other scalable storage options. Megapixel optimized, Pivot3 RAIGE (RAID Across Gigabit Ethernet) enables higher bandwidth and provides continuous availability through the failure of any disk, node or networking component. It installs in under twenty minutes and with an easy-to-understand interface can be managed by readily-available server and networking personnel. 


Products and Services
Facility Design and Construction > Surveillance > CCTV Systems > Pivot3 High Definition Storage
Pivot3 High-Definition Storage for video surveillance supports up to sixteen times the cameras at half the cost of other scalable storage options. Megapixel optimized, Pivot3 RAIGE (RAID Across Gigabit Ethernet) enables higher bandwidth and provides continuous availability through the failure of any disk, node or networking component. It installs in under twenty minutes and with an easy-to-understand interface can be managed by readily-available server and networking personnel.







